Description_lang: Although many varieties of Qiraji Battle Tank can still be found in the ruins of Ahn'Qiraj today, the darkest of the species were only seen on the day the Scarab gong was rung.

Name_lang: Winged Steed of the Ebon Blade

Description_lang: Even the dead need a lift every now and then.
The scourge of the slightly-northeastern seas, giant parrots like Polly can live for up to 2000 years. What a wonderful curse on your next of kin.
